&lt;p&gt;Are you motivated, committed, caring and enthusiastic about your role as a nurse? If you are versatile, hardworking and enjoy working within a multidisciplinary team then the Cardiac Suite team are looking for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a busy Cardiac unit specialising in Cardiac Angiography, Percutaneous Coronary intervention, Pacemakers and Cardiac Resynchronisation Therapy. We care for a mixture of elective out patients and acute in patients between two Cardiac Catheterisation Labs and our 9 bed recovery ward. There are also strong links to CCU and Tisbury Ward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have full time and part time Band 5 vacancies and the successful applicant needs to be flexible to the needs of the service and participate on the On Call rota. An informal visit to the unit is also advised.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
